SELECT store.name
FROM classes
INNER JOIN instructors ON instructors.teacher_id = classes.teacher_id
INNER JOIN store ON store.name = instructors.name
WHERE store.star_rating = 5 AND (instructors.teacher_age <= 84 OR classes.level = 4 AND classes.year >= 2003)

SELECT instructors.name
FROM classes
INNER JOIN instructors ON instructors.teacher_id = classes.teacher_id
INNER JOIN store ON store.name = instructors.name
WHERE (classes.class_subject = 'sociology' OR classes.class_subject = 'history' OR classes.class_subject = 'physics') AND classes.grade >= 62 AND classes.year <= 2017 AND store.star_rating = 2

SELECT instructors.name
FROM classes
INNER JOIN instructors ON instructors.teacher_id = classes.teacher_id
INNER JOIN store ON store.name = instructors.name
WHERE (instructors.teacher_age >= 59 OR (classes.class_subject = 'history' OR classes.class_subject = 'chemistry') AND classes.level = 8 AND classes.year <= 2017) AND store.location = 'NY'
